Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(无脸男)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日置藩藩士佐佐木一家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨遭灭门的血案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此宣布裁决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木家当家一正之妻蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游街示众之后\N再处以磔刑悬首示众！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨遵裁处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(前篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清冷的月光照着你徘徊的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话却说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹记那虚伪的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却那温暖的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那双失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什么样的风景？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的下弦月隐脏于云间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述说着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱着孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又将对月长叹…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来事情也就告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你一样是囚犯哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个卖药的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到一个奇怪的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我的药一点效也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还硬说我是骗子什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种一昧想靠药治病的态度\N就令人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会没有效果\N都是因为你信心不足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有句\N“精神所至金子会开”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如此反唇相讥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他就直嚷着要我还钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还告上衙门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后就落得这个下场真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…应该是\N“精诚所至金石为开”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要叫人罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不觉得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟把男人跟女人\N关在同一个牢房里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么大惊小怪反正你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经被判死罪了不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道得还真清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为街头巷尾都在谈你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你是杀死丈夫以及婆婆等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士全家的恶鬼妻子蝴蝶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们这样形容我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把四个人吊在梅树上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，奇怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？\N怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么，我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？忘了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了反正谣言总会被加油添醋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题不在于你怎么杀死他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是用味噌煮汤或盐烤\N鲭鱼还是鲭鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂您的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是我不觉得\N那是出自一个女人之手哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别在意，这只是我工作的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既无目击证词\N也没有强而有力的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单凭你自首说“是我干的”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未免太含糊不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这件事并非你一个人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:06:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得…应该是物怪干的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否…有什么头绪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是我一个人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是身上散发出来的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是该有的表情等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你根本不像\N明天将被处死之人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经换上一身白衣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…那是这里供给的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撇开服装不说\N主要是你的表情哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来仿佛变了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平常的蝴蝶小姐完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在胡说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您又不晓得\N平常的我是什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人，回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个卖药的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不过现在是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我，你是怎么进来这的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话真多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是头一次\N碰到这样的物怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人并非什么可疑之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！为什么要阻碍我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里是最安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的家伙你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被缠上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，原以为要揭露其“形”\N得花不少功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然自已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其“形”已现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是物怪的“形”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要阻碍我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里是最安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想离开此地的话此地即是牢狱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么啊？\N想留在此地的话此地即是堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想回去那个地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回…去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类更可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还是有心地善良的物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到她的话没？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限之虚空在吾之手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这样去找“形”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里应该就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵应该暂时不会追来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那些奇奇怪怪的招术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如那男人所言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了…\N把你救出那个牢狱而诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢狱？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢狱？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！拿酒来，酒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没酒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶也真是的\N早点拿来不就得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨手笨脚的媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼怪里怪气的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哥哥你干嘛娶她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她老妈苦苦哀求我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是前一个媳妇上吊自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会让这种女人进门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过娶来煮饭刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要是也能多点情趣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌~你怎么讲这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把如恶鬼般的毒全吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你会认为我这个物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲这种话很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种触感…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏那个触感才让我能够熬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次又一次，一次又一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是您救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…还是要回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量有限\N追兵很快就会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再回去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去你将会成为逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:13:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你丈夫一家\N真的会变成是你杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算回去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或是我不回去都没什么差别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不回去你这辈子都会被通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许一抓到就会被就地正法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的死法反而轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚刚在牢里的男人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个男人\N让你有这种想法的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自已不想回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意跟我在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可是您…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确，我并非人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是正如你所看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平常的模样\N跟人类并无两样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我无法摘下这个面具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要我做什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会想办法养活你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你当我的妻子吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人也可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃我这带罪之身吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这意思是你答应罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太，太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，那我们来庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶，我们一起展开新的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位~这是我的妻子喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧，是蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~真有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有办法娶蝴蝶小姐为妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕，好羡慕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺可喜可贺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺可喜可贺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群乱来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实他们一直在你身边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你没发现而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一直守护着你\N好羡慕，好羡慕哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人总是很健忘的\N可喜可贺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记曾经邂逅多少事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记自已被多少人围绕着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过之后…就不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将成为你活着的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高砂呀高砂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺，可喜可贺呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来我们就结为连理了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后我们就夫妻同心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身已将她调教得\N不管何时都不会令家门蒙羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后务必请您多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么，母亲大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么，这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出嫁…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来\N我就无愧于梅泽家的代代祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，你也快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好拜托人家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你天生就是个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭这个脸蛋再学点技艺的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是出身贫寒的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能嫁入大户人家的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~好孩子，真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！别让她看这些！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你让我看了一出好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得很开心哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那个面具…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“面”这个字代表着外表
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓人类的脸\N不过是表现于外的形罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我承认这个面具\N就是我的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个面容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就将成为我的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，脸又变了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的真面目究竟是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易…抓住的新人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩塌了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种虚伪的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是物怪为了欺骗你而安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为他是来救我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗的背后必然隐脏着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还特地戴上面具…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精心安排这出戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是隐瞒了什么吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记自已面貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现出“形”来！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待续)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你不在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法笑得开怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能将那些无可取代的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜并活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛开在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随风缓缓飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不见的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子\N将是我此生无可比喻的珍爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋脏于心中的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便存在于相同之时空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或目睹相同之景物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存于你我内心之物\N亦绝非相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我内心深处的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:22:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(无脸男)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.56,0:23:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清冷的月光照着你徘徊的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话却说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.75,0:23:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹记那虚伪的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却那温暖的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那双失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:24:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什么样的风景？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的下弦月隐脏于云间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.14,0:24:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述说着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱着孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又将对月长叹…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(后篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂能如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.11,0:24:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你不愿现出原形…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.14,0:24:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.25,0:24:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.55,0:24:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.42,0:24:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.82,0:24:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安份一下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.69,0:24:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.27,0:25:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.47,0:25:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.64,0:25:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么刚刚的戏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.48,0:25:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续演下去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.12,0:25:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪的“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.02,0:25:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是基于人的渊源跟因果形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.33,0:25:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当妖怪感应到人类的感情或执念
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.86,0:25:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪就会变成物怪\N对了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.13,0:25:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说过您是来斩除物怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.17,0:25:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在就能斩除的话\N我也是十分乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.24,0:25:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是物怪的真与理…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.88,0:25:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有若缺少形的话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.35,0:25:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔剑是无法拔出的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.86,0:26:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.09,0:26:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻烦啊！物怪这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.76,0:26:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真”乃事情的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.40,0:26:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”乃心的样貌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.47,0:26:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若物怪不现出他的“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.11,0:26:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我只得请你…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.51,0:26:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细道出真与理
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.95,0:26:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.39,0:26:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.06,0:26:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…一生？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.70,0:26:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！拿酒来，酒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.57,0:26:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没酒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.67,0:26:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.27,0:26:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.51,0:26:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨手笨脚的媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.91,0:26:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.34,0:26:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个怪里怪气的家伙\N物怪看上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.95,0:27:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讨人厌真讨人厌\N就是你这种情绪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.05,0:27:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讨人厌真讨人厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.13,0:27:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…对物怪来说\N你非常适合他附身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.70,0:27:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.43,0:27:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这确实很可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.40,0:27:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.84,0:27:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这可笑之事，你…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.08,0:27:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.54,0:27:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了多少人？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.92,0:27:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于物怪力量的下场即是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.95,0:27:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.22,0:27:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...你还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.03,0:27:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.00,0:27:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错就是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.07,0:27:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每天不停仰望的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.04,0:28:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片只属于你的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.41,0:28:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于我的...天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.48,0:28:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.09,0:28:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.97,0:28:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.45,0:28:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是...看着它
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.12,0:28:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看着天空\N我就已经觉得很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.35,0:28:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...不离开这里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.29,0:28:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.96,0:28:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正杀死的人...是谁？\N闭...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.57,0:29:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正...杀死的人？\N闭...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.81,0:29:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.61,0:29:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.04,0:29:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.78,0:29:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.98,0:29:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.15,0:29:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再踏入蝴蝶小姐的内心！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.13,0:29:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.79,0:29:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想离开此地的话此地即是牢狱
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.43,0:29:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想留在此地的话此地即是堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.00,0:29:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里跟那里都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.74,0:29:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直认为此处是监牢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.48,0:29:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.75,0:29:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.69,0:29:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.73,0:30:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.30,0:30:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...为什么不逃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.55,0:30:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.29,0:30:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟以前的我\N简直就是一个模子印出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.16,0:30:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这样美丽的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.93,0:30:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能嫁入武士之家的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.37,0:30:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.40,0:30:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.77,0:30:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.54,0:30:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...最喜欢母亲大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.42,0:30:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了，蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.79,0:31:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.06,0:31:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.86,0:31:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是假的！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.99,0:31:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.96,0:31:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戏正要上演
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.37,0:31:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.07,0:31:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二幕
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.64,0:31:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你天生就是个美人\N这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.34,0:31:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭这个脸蛋再学点技艺的话\N母亲大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.85,0:31:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是出身贫寒的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.65,0:31:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能嫁入大户人家的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.82,0:31:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.99,0:31:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~好孩子，真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.86,0:31:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢母亲大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.86,0:31:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望让她开心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.27,0:31:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在忍耐吗？\N咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.37,0:31:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜牺牲自已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.64,0:31:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...心？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.21,0:32:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说这么多次了你还是不懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.12,0:32:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.55,0:32:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿你不是练好几次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.25,0:32:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.16,0:32:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.22,0:32:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次，从头开始\N对不起，对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.56,0:32:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你怎么嫁入武士之家？\N对不起，对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.20,0:32:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，再来一遍\N对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.54,0:32:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.55,0:32:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.23,0:32:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了！快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.27,0:32:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身已将她调教得\N不管何时都不会令家门蒙羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.04,0:33:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.68,0:33:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.14,0:33:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三幕
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.08,0:33:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还请各位多多照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.42,0:33:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.28,0:33:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把头抬起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.69,0:33:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样拼命恳求
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.52,0:33:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会害我过意不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.69,0:33:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会茶道，弹琴跟花道是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.86,0:33:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚上会像荡妇一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.90,0:33:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦，那要看大哥怎么调教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.47,0:33:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼\N女人只要有钱还怕找不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.34,0:33:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.80,0:33:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后务必请您多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.84,0:33:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲的愿望...吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.51,0:33:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N请各位务必多多照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.84,0:33:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人很早就过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.41,0:33:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俸禄也跟着停止
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.18,0:33:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于失去一切的母亲来说
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.75,0:33:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我嫁入武士之家
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.25,0:33:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她的生存意义
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.66,0:33:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来\N我就无愧于梅泽家的代代祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.26,0:33:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.73,0:34:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就成了\N替母亲实现愿望的工具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.77,0:34:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.14,0:34:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然那又是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.81,0:34:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.15,0:34:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.99,0:34:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.92,0:34:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了母亲的愿望\N而压抑自已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.99,0:34:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但身为工具的你却...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.00,0:34:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.80,0:34:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.00,0:34:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你恋爱的对象...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.84,0:34:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.68,0:34:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.81,0:34:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.51,0:34:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四幕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.28,0:34:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.02,0:34:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.52,0:34:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶也真是的\N早点拿来不就得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.69,0:35:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨手笨脚的媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.93,0:35:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼怪里怪气的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.63,0:35:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哥哥你干嘛娶她？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.20,0:35:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她老妈苦苦哀求我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.17,0:35:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是前一个媳妇上吊自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.51,0:35:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会让这种女人进门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.84,0:35:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过娶来做饭刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.55,0:35:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要是也能多点情趣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.02,0:35:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌~你怎么讲这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.47,0:35:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.91,0:35:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.61,0:35:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.51,0:35:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.68,0:35:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.25,0:36:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.99,0:36:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.82,0:36:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.83,0:36:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...别问了...别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.93,0:36:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再问了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.31,0:36:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.62,0:36:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐那个面具...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.75,0:36:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.29,0:36:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是物怪操控那个戴面具的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.13,0:36:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗了你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.10,0:36:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并把你束缚在那个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.97,0:36:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“真“
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.45,0:36:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.25,0:37:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而接受了母亲扭曲的爱\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.22,0:37:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致你的心也跟着扭曲\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.72,0:37:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是被物怪缠上\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.16,0:37:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“理“
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.77,0:37:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...最喜欢母亲大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.67,0:37:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.78,0:37:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有认真练习吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.58,0:37:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能嫁入豪门
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.65,0:37:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...已经很努力了\N我也会引以为傲的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.28,0:37:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很努力...很努力了\N之后再生个健康的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.75,0:37:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.75,0:37:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要我不要...\N为了得到夫家的疼爱
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.96,0:37:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要我不要啊...\N你一定要拼个儿子出来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.16,0:37:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人听我说...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.36,0:37:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待啊~\N母亲大人你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.74,0:38:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水天宫的符好像很有用呢\N母亲大人听我说...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.44,0:38:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人你听我说啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.24,0:38:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让他弟弟抢先的话\N那就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.31,0:38:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人为什么不听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.75,0:38:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说听我说啊...\N所以你一定要先生出小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.72,0:38:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说...\N啊~真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.76,0:38:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说好不好\N好期待哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.90,0:38:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N好期待哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.73,0:38:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.64,0:38:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.97,0:38:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直跟白痴一样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.78,0:38:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.05,0:38:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.75,0:38:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.02,0:38:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.17,0:39:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.31,0:39:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自已？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.81,0:39:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.72,0:39:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了他人的欲望\N我杀了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.59,0:39:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记自已面貌的...\N我...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.72,0:39:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪\N杀了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.12,0:39:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现出...形来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.07,0:39:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自已！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.67,0:39:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.34,0:39:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.43,0:40:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后可以问件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.63,0:40:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无脸男为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.81,0:40:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要救我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.68,0:40:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得自已得救了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.69,0:40:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.39,0:40:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.13,0:40:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱上你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.00,0:40:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.94,0:40:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是个无法实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.51,0:40:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.21,0:40:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.28,0:40:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的...物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.06,0:41:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.94,0:41:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.05,0:41:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.52,0:41:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.12,0:41:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶也真是的\N早点拿来不就得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.82,0:41:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨手笨脚的媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.42,0:41:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼怪里怪气的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.66,0:41:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哥哥你干嘛娶她？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.80,0:41:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她老妈苦苦哀求我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.57,0:41:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是前一个媳妇上吊自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.14,0:41:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会让这种女人进门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.61,0:41:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过娶来做饭刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.38,0:41:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要是也能多点情趣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.71,0:42:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌~你怎么讲这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.52,0:42:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.91,0:42:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你还在干麻啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.31,0:42:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了...真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.45,0:42:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错\N实在是怪里怪气的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.86,0:42:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，蝴蝶\N真讨人厌...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.26,0:42:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聋啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.40,0:42:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.00,0:42:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什么事情都拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.97,0:42:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点用也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.14,0:42:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得她在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.24,0:43:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是怎么教的！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.88,0:43:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶，快把酒拿来！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.01,0:43:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点拿来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.15,0:43:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.35,0:43:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.96,0:43:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.16,0:43:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.91,0:43:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(完)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.95,0:43:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你不在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.59,0:43:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法笑得开怀
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.39,0:43:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.86,0:44:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.20,0:44:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能将那些无可取代的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.94,0:44:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜并活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.81,0:44:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.26,0:44:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛开在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.36,0:44:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随风缓缓飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.74,0:44:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不见的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.28,0:44:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子\N将是我此生无可比喻的珍爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
